headline.main: Tottenham and Man City Keep Up the Chase
headline.print_headline: Tottenham and Man City Keep Up the Chase

lead_paragraph: East Libyan forces resumed air strikes against rival factions on Sunday as they tried to push them back from positions around the major oil terminals of Es Sider and Ras Lanuf, a military spokesman said.
